  <h1>Benchmarks</h1>
  <p class="muted">Methodology notes for latency/throughput measurements and reproducible runs.</p>

  <h2>Latency</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Report p50/p95/p99 and sample size (N)</li>
    <li>Specify region, network path, and payload size</li>
    <li>Clarify scope: gateway request → signed response</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Throughput</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Publish only with full harness + host specs (CPU/RAM), limits, concurrency</li>
    <li>Include error rates and backpressure behavior</li>
  </ul>

